leads.lead_text: Leaves usually widest below middle; upper leaf surface glabrous, smooth or slightly wrinkled; lower surface with pale hairs, rarely glabrous; midrib obscure; margin recurved
Leaves widest at middle; upper leaf surface tuberculate; lower surface glabrous with prominent midrib; margin thickened and tuberculate but not recurved
